A cyberpunk digital workspace floating in a neon-lit void, showing multiple holographic application windows cascading in layers of importance—a massive dominant screen in the center glowing bright cyan displaying abstract workflow patterns, surrounded by smaller, dimmer auxiliary floating panels in purple and magenta hues. A single user silhouette sits before this digital constellation, their attention clearly focused on the central sovereign display. Circuit-like streams of data flow between the windows, with the brightest streams connecting to the primary application. The scene has deep shadows, rain-slicked reflective surfaces below, and the characteristic pink and blue color palette of cyberpunk aesthetics. The composition emphasizes hierarchy and focus through size, brightness, and positioning of the floating interfaces.
